            "value": "In Zend\/Db\/Adapter\/Driver\/Pdo\/Statement.php on line 218 when throwing an InvalidQueryException it tries to access $this->resource->error for the exception message.\r\n\r\nPDO and PDOStatement have \"errorCode\" [1] and \"errorInfo\" [2] methods for getting information about the errors.\r\n\r\nI am\/was testing with beta3 and Rob Allen's ZF2 tutorial.\r\n\r\nPull request is on it's way.\r\n\r\nphp -v\r\nPHP 5.3.10\r\n\r\n[1] http:\/\/www.php.net\/manual\/en\/pdostatement.errorcode.php\r\n[2] http:\/\/www.php.net\/manual\/en\/pdostatement.errorinfo.php"
